ble.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/289902/', '', 'Golimumab, Cyclosporine, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, More', 'Acetaminophen, Ibuprofen, Celecoxib, Acetylsalicylic acid, Naloxone', 1767369485);
